Package: taskr
Type: Package
Title: Modern Task Runner for R Projects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fabian", "Distler", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A modern, cross-platform task runner for R projects. Similar to
    'Taskfile' or 'just', but designed specifically for R workflows. Supports
    task dependencies, file change detection, and seamless integration with
    R package development tools.
